title: The Greatest Smash Ultimate Player of All Time - The Story of MkLeo

media:group.media:title: The Greatest Smash Ultimate Player of All Time - The Story of MkLeo
media:group.media:description:
Leonardo Lopez Perez, better known by his tag, MkLeo, is a Super Smash Bros player from Mexico City, Mexico. Born in 2001, Leo started playing Smash Bros at a young age and began competing not long after.

In today's video, we dive into the competitive career of MkLeo and the story of how he became known as one of the greatest Smash Ultimate players of all time.
